	fink-package-precedence,
	gcc9,
	libjpeg9,
	szip
<<
Depends: <<
	libjpeg9-shlibs,
	szip-shlibs
<<
Source: https://support.hdfgroup.org/ftp/HDF/releases/HDF%v/src/hdf-%v.tar.bz2
